criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients referred to the ''Institut Universitaire de Cardiologie et Pneumologie de
             Québec'' 's sleep clinic who have undergone a cardiorespiratory polygraphy.

          -  Body mass index (BMI) between 27-35 kg/m2;

          -  Apnea-Hypopnea Index (ADI) equal or above 20 events per hour with less than 5 events
             per hour of central origin;

          -  Oxygen Desaturaton Index (ODI) equal or above 10 events per hour;

          -  Percentage of time spent below 90% of oxygen saturation equal or less than 10%

        Exclusion criteria :

        - Patients not meeting the above inclusion criteria.
